column5: Well i got the winter blues. So i thought that i would post a pic of some new lures that i have picked up recently. 1 Jake, 1 Xrap, 1 jointed shad rap, 1 minnow rap, and 2 lucky crafts.
That collection includes two of my go-to baits (shad rap and pointer).  Some good colors too.  I bet that ran you about $70, though.  It sure adds up fast (much to my wife's dismay)  Lumberjack
Fishing show up here next week!  :-)
i really like the looks of those minnow raps, they should work well.
Nice choices on the Lucky Crafts.
I like that jointed shad!  I picked up a few new ones the other day... x-rap deep. Can't wait to try them.  Glass Ghost, Hot head, Purple Gold, Rainbow Trout
